# Deployment — {{project_name}}

This monorepo deploys two surfaces:

- **API** — Hono on Cloudflare Workers via Wrangler.
- **Web** — Vite static build, hostable on Cloudflare Pages, GitHub Pages, or Docker/Nginx.

## API: Cloudflare Workers

One-time setup:

```bash
pnpm --filter @{{project_slug}}/api exec wrangler login
```

Configure bindings in `apps/api/wrangler.toml` (KV, D1, R2, Durable Objects, etc.) before deploying.

Deploy:

```bash
pnpm run deploy:api
```

Local dev:

```bash
pnpm --filter @{{project_slug}}/api run dev
```

The web app's `vite.config.ts` proxies `/api/*` to `http://localhost:8787` so you can run both surfaces concurrently with:

```bash
pnpm dev
```

## Web: Cloudflare Pages (recommended)

Connect the repo in the Cloudflare dashboard with these settings:

- Build command: `pnpm install && pnpm --filter @{{project_slug}}/web run build`
- Build output directory: `apps/web/dist`

Set `VITE_API_BASE_URL` in Pages environment variables to the deployed Workers URL.

## Web: Docker fallback

```bash
pnpm run docker:build
docker run --rm -p 8080:80 {{docker_namespace}}/{{project_slug}}:latest
```

Tags produced:

```text
{{docker_namespace}}/{{project_slug}}:<package version>
{{docker_namespace}}/{{project_slug}}:latest
```

## Verification

```bash
pnpm run verify
```

For Workers config changes:

```bash
pnpm --filter @{{project_slug}}/api exec wrangler deploy --dry-run
```

For Docker changes:

```bash
pnpm run docker:build
```
